	<h1 class="title">这个时代，图书馆要是颜值不高，连拍照背景墙都轮不上</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-20 14:13:02 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16269/medium/16269.jpg?1445239167" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16269" data-title="《这个时代，图书馆要是颜值不高，连拍照背景墙都轮不上》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16269/medium/16269.jpg?1445239167" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16269.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
